payload.text: Ambitious Software Engineer who loves when a plan comes together. With 10+ years of experience in companies and startups, mainly in the trucking industry. During this time, worked on many projects with different roles which helped in developing a whole picture of the entire production process. Always trying to balance the ideal with what is realistic and what brings revenue.

descriptionPoints: responsible for the ports industry where we successfully reduced turn times by 20%
maintaining and improving the core booking process and trying to stay on top of feature requests coming from the events industry
involved in splitting the old monolithic system into scalable microservices so that the system could survive a fast growth of the client base

paragraphs.title: Senior Software Engineer Team Lead at TruckTrack

directly communicating with clients about the implementation and feature requests
